event.title: April Meetup
event.description:
Welcome all to the April SWMobile Meetup.

We have three great talks lined up for you:

- Jake Chandrasakera & Pete Horsham (TBD)
- Harry Jordan - Building a Photo Editor (iOS)
- Kentaro Takiguchi - Challenges working on a long running app

We'll be hosted by Cookpad who will also kindly be providing food and drink on the evening.

- Doors will open at 6:30pm

- Food and drink will be available.

- Talks will start at 7pm.

After the event, we'll move on to a pub to continue the discussions. üç∑

Speakers have been updated for this meetup now, but if you do have a talk that you'd like to present at a future meetup then please do get in touch via http://cfp.swmobile.org, [masked] or via message on this group.
